Throughout the year, I demonstrated strong ownership, adaptability, and collaboration across multiple initiatives. I began by contributing to LH360 while also supporting the team on SQL-related improvements. I worked closely with developers to strengthen their understanding of database structures, review SQL changes, and guide them toward more efficient query design and better data-handling practices.

